---
title: "_applyAllowlistedTargetsUpdates (WorkflowRouter)"
---
stateDiagram-v2
    direction TB
    [*] --> q_check_wf: check workflowId allowlisted
    q_check_wf --> q_revert_wf: !s_allowlistedWorkflowIds.contains(workflowId)
    q_revert_wf --> [*]: revert WorkflowIdNotAllowlisted(workflowId)
    q_check_wf --> q_check_empty: workflowId is allowlisted
    q_check_empty --> q_revert_empty: removes.length == 0 AND adds.length == 0
    q_revert_empty --> [*]: revert EmptyList()
    q_check_empty --> q_remove_loop: at least one list non-empty
    q_remove_loop --> q_remove_body: i < removes.length
    q_remove_loop --> q_add_loop: i >= removes.length
    q_remove_body --> q_cast_selectors: target = removes[i]
    q_cast_selectors --> q_remove_selectors: cast bytes32[] to bytes4[] via assembly
    q_remove_selectors --> q_remove_target: _applyAllowlistedSelectorsUpdates(workflowId, target, allSelectors, empty)
    q_remove_target --> q_emit_target_removed: allowlistedTargets.remove(target)
    q_emit_target_removed --> q_remove_loop: emit TargetRemovedFromAllowlist(workflowId, target); i++
    q_add_loop --> q_add_body: i < adds.length
    q_add_loop --> [*]: i >= adds.length
    q_add_body --> q_check_zero_addr: target = adds[i].target
    q_check_zero_addr --> q_revert_zero: target == address(0)
    q_revert_zero --> [*]: revert InvalidZeroAddress()
    q_check_zero_addr --> q_add_target: target != address(0)
    q_add_target --> q_add_selectors: allowlistedTargets.add(target)
    q_add_selectors --> q_add_loop: _applyAllowlistedSelectorsUpdates(workflowId, target, empty, adds[i].selectors); i++

    note right of q_check_wf
        INV-001: workflowId must already be in s_allowlistedWorkflowIds
        INV-002: removes processed before adds
        INV-003: removing a target cascades to remove all its selectors first
    end note

    note right of q_cast_selectors
        INV-004: assembly cast from bytes32[] to bytes4[] is safe because both are memory arrays with 32-byte slots
        INV-005: target is removed from set AFTER its selectors are cleaned up
    end note
